Reviewer #1: I've really appreciated this study! I believe it provides new
 insight in the reversible adhesion mechanism in insects, which may be of
 interest also for engineering applications.
 It is also well written and relatively easy to follow.
 However I have a some questions the authors should address before the paper
 may be accepted for publication.
 
\end_layout

